{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WN18kY8HzsR6hp5pHvnyqV","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n     2→<persistence xmlns=\"http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/persistence\"\n     3→  xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" version=\"2.1\"\n     4→  xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/persistence http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/persistence/persistence_2_1.xsd\">\n     5→  <persistence-unit name=\"CargoTrackerUnit\">\n     6→    <jta-data-source>java:app/jdbc/CargoTrackerDatabase</jta-data-source>\n     7→    <shared-cache-mode>ALL</shared-cache-mode>\n     8→    <properties>\n     9→      <!-- The default behavior is not generating a schema. Schema generation is \n    10→        good for demos, RAD, development, etc but likely not a good idea for production. -->\n    11→      <property\n    12→        name=\"javax.persistence.schema-generation.database.action\"\n    13→        value=\"create\" />\n    14→      <!-- This will fail if it's not invoked on a blank database - this is fine. \n    15→        What this does is insert a single record that the application settings check can \n    16→        place a pessimistic lock on. -->\n    17→      <property name=\"javax.persistence.sql-load-script-source\"\n    18→        value=\"META-INF/initital-data.sql\" />\n    19→      <!-- The default log level of info is best for production, want to see verbose \n    20→        output for development. -->\n    21→      <property name=\"eclipselink.logging.level\" value=\"FINEST\" />\n    22→    </properties>\n    23→  </persistence-unit>\n    24→</persistence>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_013qNWyZ5fyowcB7WtsTxu7o","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"419ce276-3ba4-405e-a894-4fd28d1069ae"}
