n\n#### Domain Model - Handling (9 files)\n23-31. All handling events including HandlingEvent, HandlingEventFactory, HandlingEventRepository, HandlingHistory, and exception classes\n\n#### Domain Model - Location (4 files)\n32-35. Location, UnLocode, LocationRepository, SampleLocations\n\n#### Domain Model - Voyage (6 files)\n36-41. Voyage, VoyageNumber, Schedule, CarrierMovement, VoyageRepository, SampleVoyages\n\n#### Domain Shared & Service (7 files)\n42-48. Specification pattern classes, DomainObjectUtils, RoutingService interface\n\n#### Infrastructure Layer (19+ files)\n- Persistence (JPA repositories for Cargo, HandlingEvent, Location, Voyage)\n- Messaging (JMS consumers for various cargo events)\n- Routing (ExternalRoutingService)\n- Events (CDI event qualifiers)\n- Logging (LoggerProducer)\n\n####  Interface Layer (37+ files)\n- Booking facade & DTOs\n- Booking web controllers\n- Booking SSE services\n- Handling interfaces (file processing, REST, mobile)\n- Tracking web adapters\n- JSF configuration\n\n#### Pathfinder API (4 files)\n- GraphTraversalService, TransitPath, TransitEdge, GraphDao\n\n### KEY RESOURCE FILES:\n\n1. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml` - JPA configuration\n2. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/initital-data.sql` - Database initialization\n3. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/resources/META-INF/batch-jobs/EventFilesProcessorJob.xml` - Batch job configuration\n4. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/resources/org/eclipse/cargotracker/messages.properties` - I18N messag