ou can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WEK4wM3YRbR63Srf398MzT","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"5fd76ebb-e547-45ea-b080-393635082b93"}
