"trackingId\", trackingId)\n    37→          .getSingleResult();\n    38→    } catch (NoResultException e) {\n    39→      logger.log(Level.FINE, \"Find called on non-existant tracking ID.\", e);\n    40→      cargo = null;\n    41→    }\n    42→    return cargo;\n    43→  }\n    44→\n    45→  @Override\n    46→  public List<Cargo> findAll() {\n    47→    return entityManager.createNamedQuery(\"Cargo.findAll\", Cargo.class).getResultList();\n    48→  }\n    49→\n    50→  @Override\n    51→  public void store(Cargo cargo) {\n    52→    cargo.getItinerary().getLegs().forEach(leg -> entityManager.persist(leg));\n    53→    entityManager.persist(cargo);\n    54→    eventPublisher.publishEvent(new CargoUpdatedEvent(cargo));\n    55→  }\n    56→\n    57→  @Override\n    58→  public TrackingId nextTrackingId() {\n    59→    String random = UUID.randomUUID().toString().toUpperCase();\n    60→    return new TrackingId(random.substring(0, random.indexOf(\"-\")));\n    61→  }\n    62→}\n    63→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Jdu9B8SXASz47P5JwbEWbb","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"f400023b-e960-4edf-a112-672802de98d3"}
