{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01KhmE1DhzTn2EKQVW8SAwmW","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All the key files have been properly migrated. Let me create a summary document of all the files that were written:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all the interfaces layer files from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot 2.7.x. Here's a comprehensive summary of what was accomplished:\n\n### Migration Summary\n\nAll interfaces layer files have been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot 2.7.x. The following key transformations were applied:\n\n#### Annotation Migrations:\n- **JAX-RS → Spring MVC**: \n  - `@Path` → `@RestController` + `@RequestMapping`\n  - `@GET` → `@GetMapping`\n  - `@POST` → `@PostMapping`\n  - `@QueryParam` → `@RequestParam`\n  - `@Consumes/@Produces` → Handled automatically by Spring MVC\n  - `@XmlRootElement` → Removed (Jackson handles JSON serialization)\n\n- **CDI → Spring Dependency Injection**:\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component` or `@Service`\n  - `@Stateless` → `@Service`\n\n- **Transactions**: Added `@Transactional` where needed\n\n- **Validation**: `javax.validation` annotations preserved as-is\n\n### Files Written (Total: 21 files)\n\n#### 1. Handling Layer (3 files):\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt.java` - POJO (no changes needed)\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/rest/HandlingReport.java` - Removed `@XmlRootElement`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/rest/HandlingReportService.java` - Migrated to `@RestController` with `@PostMapping`\n\n#### 2. Booking Facade (10 files):\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/BookingServiceFacade.java` - Interface (no changes)\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java` - `@Service` + `@Transactional`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/CargoRouteDtoAssembler.java` - `@Component`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/CargoStatusDtoAssembler.java` - `@Component`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler.java` - `@Component`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/LocationDtoAssembler.java` - `@Component`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/TrackingEventsDtoAssembler.java` - `@Component`\n\n#### 3. DTOs (6 files - POJOs):\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/Location.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/CargoRoute.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/CargoStatus.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/Leg.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/RouteCandidate.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/TrackingEvents.java`\n\n#### 4. Pathfinder API (4 files):\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/api/GraphTraversalService.java` - Migrated to `@RestController`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/api/TransitPath.java` - Removed `@XmlRootElement`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/api/TransitEdge.java` - POJO\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/internal/GraphDao.java` - `@Component`\n\n#### 5. Utility Classes (2 files):\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/Coordinates.java` - POJO (no changes)\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/CoordinatesFactory.java` - Utility class (no changes)\n\n### Key REST Endpoints Created:\n\n1. **Handling Events**: `/api/handling/reports` (POST)\n2. **Graph Traversal**: `/api/graph-traversal/shortest-path` (GET)\n\n### Notes:\n- All DTOs use Jackson for JSON serialization (no JAXB needed)\n- The original file structure and package hierarchy were preserved\n- All validation annotations (`javax.validation.*`) were kept intact\n- The DTO layer uses Location objects (not simple strings) to maintain rich domain model\n- Transaction management is handled by Spring's `@Transactional` annotation\n- All Jakarta EE annotations have been successfully replaced with Spring equivalents"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"377986f1-c410-4d1f-bf17-34e666933123"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01MBKUWb8efLtqgDcgcojXnp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01KA4rjZSPt9uJKSZLoA5JVE","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/SampleVoyages.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.voyage;\n\nimport java.lang.reflect.Field;\nimport java.time.LocalDateTime;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.Collections;\nimport java.util.HashMap;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Map;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.Location;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.SampleLocations;\n\n/** Sample carrier movements, for demo/test purposes. */\npublic class SampleVoyages {\n\n  public static final Voyage CM001 =\n      createVoyage(\"CM001\", SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM, SampleLocations.HAMBURG);\n  public static final Voyage CM002 =\n      createVoyage(\"CM002\", SampleLocations.HAMBURG, SampleLocations.HONGKONG);\n  public static final Voyage CM003 =\n      createVoyage(\"CM003\", SampleLocations.HONGKONG, SampleLocations.NEWYORK);\n  public static final Voyage CM004 =\n      createVoyage(\"CM004\", SampleLocations.NEWYORK, SampleLocations.CHICAGO);\n  public static final Voyage CM005 =\n      createVoyage(\"CM005\", SampleLocations.CHICAGO, SampleLocations.HAMBURG);\n  public static final Voyage CM006 =\n      createVoyage(\"CM006\", SampleLocations.HAMBURG, SampleLocations.HANGZOU);\n  public static final Voyage v100 =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V100\"), SampleLocations.HONGKONG)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.TOKYO,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(3).plusHours(6),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(5).plusHours(18))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.NEWYORK,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(6).plusHours(11),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(9).plusHours(11))\n          .build();\n  public static final Voyage v200 =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V200\"), SampleLocations.TOKYO)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.NEWYORK,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(6).plusHours(14),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(8).plusHours(7))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.CHICAGO,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(10).plusHours(21),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(2))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(1),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(16).plusHours(23))\n          .build();\n  public static final Voyage v300 =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V300\"), SampleLocations.TOKYO)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.ROTTERDAM,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(8).plusHours(8),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(11).plusHours(16))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HAMBURG,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(11).plusHours(4),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(12).plusHours(17))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.MELBOURNE,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(9),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(18).plusHours(10))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.TOKYO,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(19).plusHours(17),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(21).plusHours(4))\n          .build();\n  public static final Voyage v400 =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V400\"), SampleLocations.HAMBURG)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(9),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(15).plusHours(18))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HELSINKI,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(15).plusHours(11),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(16).plusHours(16))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HAMBURG,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(20).plusHours(18),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(22).plusHours(9))\n          .build();\n  /**\n   * Voyage number 0100S (by ship)\n   *\n   * <p>Hongkong - Hangzou - Tokyo - Melbourne - New York\n   */\n  public static final Voyage HONGKONG_TO_NEW_YORK =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0100S\"), SampleLocations.HONGKONG)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HANGZOU,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(1).plusHours(12),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(3)\n                  .plusHours(14)\n                  .plusMinutes(30))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.TOKYO,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(4).plusHours(21),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(6)\n                  .plusHours(6)\n                  .plusMinutes(15))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.MELBOURNE,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(9).plusHours(11),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(12)\n                  .plusHours(11)\n                  .plusMinutes(30))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.NEWYORK,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(14).plusHours(12),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(23)\n                  .plusHours(23)\n                  .plusMinutes(10))\n          .build();\n  /**\n   * Voyage number 0200T (by train)\n   *\n   * <p>New York - Chicago - Dallas\n   */\n  public static final Voyage NEW_YORK_TO_DALLAS =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0200T\"), SampleLocations.NEWYORK)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.CHICAGO,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(24).plusHours(7),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(24)\n                  .plusHours(17)\n                  .plusMinutes(45))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.DALLAS,\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(24)\n                  .plusHours(21)\n                  .plusMinutes(25),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(25)\n                  .plusHours(19)\n                  .plusMinutes(30))\n          .build();\n  /**\n   * Voyage number 0300A (by airplane)\n   *\n   * <p>Dallas - Hamburg - Stockholm - Helsinki\n   */\n  public static final Voyage DALLAS_TO_HELSINKI =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0300A\"), SampleLocations.DALLAS)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HAMBURG,\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(29)\n                  .plusHours(3)\n                  .plusMinutes(30),\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(31).plusHours(14))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM,\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(1)\n                  .plusHours(15)\n                  .plusMinutes(20),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(1)\n                  .plusHours(18)\n                  .plusMinutes(40))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HELSINKI,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(11).plusDays(2).plusHours(9),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(2)\n                  .plusHours(11)\n                  .plusMinutes(15))\n          .build();\n  /**\n   * Voyage number 0301S (by ship)\n   *\n   * <p>Dallas - Hamburg - Stockholm - Helsinki, alternate route\n   */\n  public static final Voyage DALLAS_TO_HELSINKI_ALT =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0301S\"), SampleLocations.DALLAS)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HELSINKI,\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(10)\n                  .plusDays(29)\n                  .plusHours(3)\n                  .plusMinutes(30),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(5)\n                  .plusHours(15)\n                  .plusMinutes(45))\n          .build();\n  /**\n   * Voyage number 0400S (by ship)\n   *\n   * <p>Helsinki - Rotterdam - Shanghai - Hongkong\n   */\n  public static final Voyage HELSINKI_TO_HONGKONG =\n      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0400S\"), SampleLocations.HELSINKI)\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.ROTTERDAM,\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(4)\n                  .plusHours(5)\n                  .plusMinutes(50),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(6)\n                  .plusHours(14)\n                  .plusMinutes(10))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.SHANGHAI,\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(10)\n                  .plusHours(21)\n                  .plusMinutes(45),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(22)\n                  .plusHours(16)\n                  .plusMinutes(40))\n          .addMovement(\n              SampleLocations.HONGKONG,\n              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(11).plusDays(24).plusHours(7),\n              LocalDateTime.now()\n                  .minusYears(1)\n                  .plusMonths(11)\n                  .plusDays(28)\n                  .plusHours(13)\n                  .plusMinutes(37))\n          .build();\n\n  public static final Map<VoyageNumber, Voyage> ALL = new HashMap<>();\n\n  static {\n    for (Field field : SampleVoyages.class.getDeclaredFields()) {\n      if (field.getType().equals(Voyage.class)) {\n        try {\n          Voyage voyage = (Voyage) field.get(null);\n          ALL.put(voyage.getVoyageNumber(), voyage);\n        } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {\n          throw new RuntimeException(e);\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  private static Voyage createVoyage(String id, Location from, Location to) {\n    return new Voyage(\n        new VoyageNumber(id),\n        new Schedule(\n            Collections.singletonList(\n                new CarrierMovement(from, to, LocalDateTime.now(), LocalDateTime.now()))));\n  }\n\n  public static List<Voyage> getAll() {\n    return new ArrayList<>(ALL.values());\n  }\n\n  public static Voyage lookup(VoyageNumber voyageNumber) {\n    return ALL.get(voyageNumber);\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8254,"cache_read_input_tokens":108663,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8254,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5015},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WEK4wM3YRbR63Srf398MzT","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"8ac8bf08-9da3-4033-a19d-147c2fd9cf64"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01MBKUWb8efLtqgDcgcojXnp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01J5YjBX22YrsXdp4WitnChX","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/DomainObjectUtils.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.shared;\n\n// TODO [Clean Code] Make this a CDI singleton?\npublic class DomainObjectUtils {\n\n  /** Prevent instantiation. */\n  private DomainObjectUtils() {}\n\n  /**\n   * @param actual actual value\n   * @param safe a null-safe value\n   * @param <T> type\n   * @return actual value, if it's not null, or safe value if the actual value is null.\n   */\n  public static <T> T nullSafe(T actual, T safe) {\n    return actual == null ? safe : actual;\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8254,"cache_read_input_tokens":108663,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8254,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5015},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WEK4wM3YRbR63Srf398MzT","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"7ae7a0d9-81a4-47e1-8e90-530081ebf530"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01MBKUWb8efLtqgDcgcojXnp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01DNWoH4EmEGhHHfnaKp6o9h","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/Specification.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.shared;\n\n/**\n * Specification interface.\n *\n * <p>Use {@link AbstractSpecification} as base for creating specifications, and only the method\n * {@link #isSatisfiedBy(Object)} must be implemented.\n */\npublic interface Specification<T> {\n\n  /**\n   * Check if {@code t} is satisfied by the specification.\n   *\n   * @param t Object to test.\n   * @return {@code true} if {@code t} satisfies the specification.\n   */\n  boolean isSatisfiedBy(T t);\n\n  /**\n   * Create a new specification that is the AND operation of {@code this} specification and another\n   * specification.\n   *\n   * @param specification Specification to AND.\n   * @return A new specification.\n   */\n  Specification<T> and(Specification<T> specification);\n\n  /**\n   * Create a new specification that is the OR operation of {@code this} specification and another\n   * specification.\n   *\n   * @param specification Specification to OR.\n   * @return A new specification.\n   */\n  Specification<T> or(Specification<T> specification);\n\n  /**\n   * Create a new specification that is the NOT operation of {@code this} specification.\n   *\n   * @param specification Specification to NOT.\n   * @return A new specification.\n   */\n  Specification<T> not(Specification<T> specification);\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8254,"cache_read_input_tokens":108663,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8254,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5015},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WEK4wM3YRbR63Srf398MzT","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"39cfdf81-fbb7-4583-ba15-20fc6218a551"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01MBKUWb8efLtqgDcgcojXnp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_015MWhTAHbJsKbPEKyyLURbg","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/AbstractSpecification.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.shared;\n\n/**\n * Abstract base implementation of composite {@link Specification} with default implementations for\n * {@code and}, {@code or} and {@code not}.\n */\npublic abstract class AbstractSpecification<T> implements Specification<T> {\n\n  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n  @Override\n  public abstract boolean isSatisfiedBy(T t);\n\n  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n  @Override\n  public Specification<T> and(Specification<T> specification) {\n    return new AndSpecification<>(this, specification);\n  }\n\n  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n  @Override\n  public Specification<T> or(Specification<T> specification) {\n    return new OrSpecification<>(this, specification);\n  }\n\n  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n  @Override\n  public Specification<T> not(Specification<T> specification) {\n    return new NotSpecification<>(specification);\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8254,"cache_read_input_tokens":108663,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8254,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5015},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WEK4wM3YRbR63Srf398MzT","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"1b3d837c-ef5d-4ede-8452-f3934c8bb122"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01KA4rjZSPt9uJKSZLoA5JVE","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/SampleVoyages.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.voyage;\n     2→\n     3→import java.lang.reflect.Field;\n     4→import java.time.LocalDateTime;\n     5→import java.util.ArrayList;\n     6→import java.util.Collections;\n     7→import java.util.HashMap;\n     8→import java.util.List;\n     9→import java.util.Map;\n    10→import org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.Location;\n    11→import org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.location.SampleLocations;\n    12→\n    13→/** Sample carrier movements, for demo/test purposes. */\n    14→public class SampleVoyages {\n    15→\n    16→  public static final Voyage CM001 =\n    17→      createVoyage(\"CM001\", SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM, SampleLocations.HAMBURG);\n    18→  public static final Voyage CM002 =\n    19→      createVoyage(\"CM002\", SampleLocations.HAMBURG, SampleLocations.HONGKONG);\n    20→  public static final Voyage CM003 =\n    21→      createVoyage(\"CM003\", SampleLocations.HONGKONG, SampleLocations.NEWYORK);\n    22→  public static final Voyage CM004 =\n    23→      createVoyage(\"CM004\", SampleLocations.NEWYORK, SampleLocations.CHICAGO);\n    24→  public static final Voyage CM005 =\n    25→      createVoyage(\"CM005\", SampleLocations.CHICAGO, SampleLocations.HAMBURG);\n    26→  public static final Voyage CM006 =\n    27→      createVoyage(\"CM006\", SampleLocations.HAMBURG, SampleLocations.HANGZOU);\n    28→  public static final Voyage v100 =\n    29→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V100\"), SampleLocations.HONGKONG)\n    30→          .addMovement(\n    31→              SampleLocations.TOKYO,\n    32→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(3).plusHours(6),\n    33→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(5).plusHours(18))\n    34→          .addMovement(\n    35→              SampleLocations.NEWYORK,\n    36→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(6).plusHours(11),\n    37→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(9).plusHours(11))\n    38→          .build();\n    39→  public static final Voyage v200 =\n    40→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V200\"), SampleLocations.TOKYO)\n    41→          .addMovement(\n    42→              SampleLocations.NEWYORK,\n    43→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(6).plusHours(14),\n    44→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(8).plusHours(7))\n    45→          .addMovement(\n    46→              SampleLocations.CHICAGO,\n    47→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(10).plusHours(21),\n    48→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(2))\n    49→          .addMovement(\n    50→              SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM,\n    51→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(1),\n    52→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(16).plusHours(23))\n    53→          .build();\n    54→  public static final Voyage v300 =\n    55→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V300\"), SampleLocations.TOKYO)\n    56→          .addMovement(\n    57→              SampleLocations.ROTTERDAM,\n    58→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(8).plusHours(8),\n    59→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(11).plusHours(16))\n    60→          .addMovement(\n    61→              SampleLocations.HAMBURG,\n    62→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(11).plusHours(4),\n    63→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(12).plusHours(17))\n    64→          .addMovement(\n    65→              SampleLocations.MELBOURNE,\n    66→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(9),\n    67→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(18).plusHours(10))\n    68→          .addMovement(\n    69→              SampleLocations.TOKYO,\n    70→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(19).plusHours(17),\n    71→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(21).plusHours(4))\n    72→          .build();\n    73→  public static final Voyage v400 =\n    74→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"V400\"), SampleLocations.HAMBURG)\n    75→          .addMovement(\n    76→              SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM,\n    77→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(14).plusHours(9),\n    78→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(15).plusHours(18))\n    79→          .addMovement(\n    80→              SampleLocations.HELSINKI,\n    81→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(15).plusHours(11),\n    82→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(16).plusHours(16))\n    83→          .addMovement(\n    84→              SampleLocations.HAMBURG,\n    85→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(20).plusHours(18),\n    86→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(3).plusDays(22).plusHours(9))\n    87→          .build();\n    88→  /**\n    89→   * Voyage number 0100S (by ship)\n    90→   *\n    91→   * <p>Hongkong - Hangzou - Tokyo - Melbourne - New York\n    92→   */\n    93→  public static final Voyage HONGKONG_TO_NEW_YORK =\n    94→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0100S\"), SampleLocations.HONGKONG)\n    95→          .addMovement(\n    96→              SampleLocations.HANGZOU,\n    97→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(1).plusHours(12),\n    98→              LocalDateTime.now()\n    99→                  .minusYears(1)\n   100→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   101→                  .plusDays(3)\n   102→                  .plusHours(14)\n   103→                  .plusMinutes(30))\n   104→          .addMovement(\n   105→              SampleLocations.TOKYO,\n   106→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(4).plusHours(21),\n   107→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   108→                  .minusYears(1)\n   109→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   110→                  .plusDays(6)\n   111→                  .plusHours(6)\n   112→                  .plusMinutes(15))\n   113→          .addMovement(\n   114→              SampleLocations.MELBOURNE,\n   115→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(9).plusHours(11),\n   116→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   117→                  .minusYears(1)\n   118→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   119→                  .plusDays(12)\n   120→                  .plusHours(11)\n   121→                  .plusMinutes(30))\n   122→          .addMovement(\n   123→              SampleLocations.NEWYORK,\n   124→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(14).plusHours(12),\n   125→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   126→                  .minusYears(1)\n   127→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   128→                  .plusDays(23)\n   129→                  .plusHours(23)\n   130→                  .plusMinutes(10))\n   131→          .build();\n   132→  /**\n   133→   * Voyage number 0200T (by train)\n   134→   *\n   135→   * <p>New York - Chicago - Dallas\n   136→   */\n   137→  public static final Voyage NEW_YORK_TO_DALLAS =\n   138→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0200T\"), SampleLocations.NEWYORK)\n   139→          .addMovement(\n   140→              SampleLocations.CHICAGO,\n   141→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(24).plusHours(7),\n   142→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   143→                  .minusYears(1)\n   144→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   145→                  .plusDays(24)\n   146→                  .plusHours(17)\n   147→                  .plusMinutes(45))\n   148→          .addMovement(\n   149→              SampleLocations.DALLAS,\n   150→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   151→                  .minusYears(1)\n   152→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   153→                  .plusDays(24)\n   154→                  .plusHours(21)\n   155→                  .plusMinutes(25),\n   156→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   157→                  .minusYears(1)\n   158→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   159→                  .plusDays(25)\n   160→                  .plusHours(19)\n   161→                  .plusMinutes(30))\n   162→          .build();\n   163→  /**\n   164→   * Voyage number 0300A (by airplane)\n   165→   *\n   166→   * <p>Dallas - Hamburg - Stockholm - Helsinki\n   167→   */\n   168→  public static final Voyage DALLAS_TO_HELSINKI =\n   169→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0300A\"), SampleLocations.DALLAS)\n   170→          .addMovement(\n   171→              SampleLocations.HAMBURG,\n   172→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   173→                  .minusYears(1)\n   174→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   175→                  .plusDays(29)\n   176→                  .plusHours(3)\n   177→                  .plusMinutes(30),\n   178→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(10).plusDays(31).plusHours(14))\n   179→          .addMovement(\n   180→              SampleLocations.STOCKHOLM,\n   181→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   182→                  .minusYears(1)\n   183→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   184→                  .plusDays(1)\n   185→                  .plusHours(15)\n   186→                  .plusMinutes(20),\n   187→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   188→                  .minusYears(1)\n   189→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   190→                  .plusDays(1)\n   191→                  .plusHours(18)\n   192→                  .plusMinutes(40))\n   193→          .addMovement(\n   194→              SampleLocations.HELSINKI,\n   195→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(11).plusDays(2).plusHours(9),\n   196→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   197→                  .minusYears(1)\n   198→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   199→                  .plusDays(2)\n   200→                  .plusHours(11)\n   201→                  .plusMinutes(15))\n   202→          .build();\n   203→  /**\n   204→   * Voyage number 0301S (by ship)\n   205→   *\n   206→   * <p>Dallas - Hamburg - Stockholm - Helsinki, alternate route\n   207→   */\n   208→  public static final Voyage DALLAS_TO_HELSINKI_ALT =\n   209→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0301S\"), SampleLocations.DALLAS)\n   210→          .addMovement(\n   211→              SampleLocations.HELSINKI,\n   212→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   213→                  .minusYears(1)\n   214→                  .plusMonths(10)\n   215→                  .plusDays(29)\n   216→                  .plusHours(3)\n   217→                  .plusMinutes(30),\n   218→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   219→                  .minusYears(1)\n   220→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   221→                  .plusDays(5)\n   222→                  .plusHours(15)\n   223→                  .plusMinutes(45))\n   224→          .build();\n   225→  /**\n   226→   * Voyage number 0400S (by ship)\n   227→   *\n   228→   * <p>Helsinki - Rotterdam - Shanghai - Hongkong\n   229→   */\n   230→  public static final Voyage HELSINKI_TO_HONGKONG =\n   231→      new Voyage.Builder(new VoyageNumber(\"0400S\"), SampleLocations.HELSINKI)\n   232→          .addMovement(\n   233→              SampleLocations.ROTTERDAM,\n   234→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   235→                  .minusYears(1)\n   236→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   237→                  .plusDays(4)\n   238→                  .plusHours(5)\n   239→                  .plusMinutes(50),\n   240→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   241→                  .minusYears(1)\n   242→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   243→                  .plusDays(6)\n   244→                  .plusHours(14)\n   245→                  .plusMinutes(10))\n   246→          .addMovement(\n   247→              SampleLocations.SHANGHAI,\n   248→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   249→                  .minusYears(1)\n   250→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   251→                  .plusDays(10)\n   252→                  .plusHours(21)\n   253→                  .plusMinutes(45),\n   254→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   255→                  .minusYears(1)\n   256→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   257→                  .plusDays(22)\n   258→                  .plusHours(16)\n   259→                  .plusMinutes(40))\n   260→          .addMovement(\n   261→              SampleLocations.HONGKONG,\n   262→              LocalDateTime.now().minusYears(1).plusMonths(11).plusDays(24).plusHours(7),\n   263→              LocalDateTime.now()\n   264→                  .minusYears(1)\n   265→                  .plusMonths(11)\n   266→                  .plusDays(28)\n   267→                  .plusHours(13)\n   268→                  .plusMinutes(37))\n   269→          .build();\n   270→\n   271→  public static final Map<VoyageNumber, Voyage> ALL = new HashMap<>();\n   272→\n   273→  static {\n   274→    for (Field field : SampleVoyages.class.getDeclaredFields()) {\n   275→      if (field.getType().equals(Voyage.class)) {\n   276→        try {\n   277→          Voyage voyage = (Voyage) field.get(null);\n   278→          ALL.put(voyage.getVoyageNumber(), voyage);\n   279→        } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {\n   280→          throw new RuntimeException(e);\n   281→        }\n   282→      }\n   283→    }\n   284→  }\n   285→\n   286→  private static Voyage createVoyage(String id, Location from, Location to) {\n   287→    return new Voyage(\n   288→        new VoyageNumber(id),\n   289→        new Schedule(\n   290→            Collections.singletonList(\n   291→                new CarrierMovement(from, to, LocalDateTime.now(), LocalDateTime.now()))));\n   292→  }\n   293→\n   294→  public static List<Voyage> getAll() {\n   295→    return new ArrayList<>(ALL.values());\n   296→  }\n   297→\n   298→  public static Voyage lookup(VoyageNumber voyageNumber) {\n   299→    return ALL.get(voyageNumber);\n   300→  }\n   301→}\n   302→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WEK4wM3YRbR63Srf398MzT","session_id":"08d2657a-d0d7-410a-941f-d00e90a603b3","uuid":"ef050792-7299-4a2c-92e7-705adc8f73f2"}
